==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Herm'''

#One of the [[Channel Islands]].
#A [[phallic]] shaped [[bust]] of the [[god]] [[Hermes]].  People would rub it to [[acquire]] good luck.  Sometimes the bust would have two heads, making it a [[double]] herm.
#The [[nickname]] of Hermes Polleto, the main character in the [[graphic novel]], "The Quadruple Herm," by Josh Rose.

